  <source>Bioithas SL</source>
  <oversight_info>
    <is_fda_regulated_drug>No</is_fda_regulated_drug>
    <is_fda_regulated_device>No</is_fda_regulated_device>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A prospective case-control pilot study to evaluate the possible effect of a probiotic mixture
      in the improvement of symptoms, the reduction in the number of days of hospitalization and
      the increase in the percentage of patients with negative PCR after infection with the
      coronavirus SARS-CoV-2.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      In this study, the investigators hypothesize a positive effect of probiotic on the gut
      microbiome that could led to produce a less severe clinical evolution of the disease.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
